DECLARE
  Change your diplomatic stance toward another country.

SYNTAX
  declare <cnum> <relation>
  decl    <cnum> <relation>

DESCRIPTION
  Sets your diplomatic relationship with another country.  This
  is a one-sided declaration — the other country is notified by
  telegram but must declare their own stance separately.

  Relation levels:
    war       - declare war (you can now freely attack)
    hostile   - hostile but not war
    neutral   - neutral stance (default for new nations)
    friendly  - friendly
    allied    - allied (full cooperation)

  You can abbreviate the relation to the first letter: w h n f a

  Note: declaring war is irreversible for several updates.
  Allied status gives the other country more intelligence about you.

EXAMPLE
  declare 3 war             declare war on country 3
  declare 2 allied          offer alliance to country 2
  declare 4 neutral         return to neutral with country 4
  decl 3 w                  shorthand for war

